To print the copy of the certificate in textual form:
openssl x509 -in cert.pem -noout -text

To find the SHA1 fingerprint of the CA certificate:
openssl x509 -in root-ca.crt -sha1 -noout -fingerprint

To find the MD5 fingerprint of the CA certificate:
openssl x509 -in root-ca.crt -md5 -noout -fingerprint